Class Visitor<T>

java.lang.Object
  structures.tree.Visitor<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
CountVisitor
public class Visitor<T>
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements a genericc visitor that can take some client-specific action when a binary tree node is visited. This (default) implementation of Visitor simply prints the node data.
